data.description: The perfect fix & flip! Come to the country and enjoy this 4 bed, 2 1/2 bath home sitting on .52 acres in the farming town of Trenton. The home is opens into a large family room with fireplace. Newer flooring in most of the upstairs. Bedrooms will need new carpet and the house needs some TLC but has great potential! With a buyer that's willing to put some time and fix up and do upgrades as they go then this is the perfect house for the price. Seller has never occupied the home and being sold "AS IS". Not for a VA or FHA buyer as seller is not going to be making any repairs. Buyer to verify all information. Accepting all offers until Sunday 3/6 at 5pm and reviewing Monday . 2022-03-09
